      <title>欧洲股市小幅上涨，关注增长前景</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-23/european-stocks-muted-as-commerzbank-drops-on-deal-uncertainty</link>
      <description><![CDATA[投资者权衡经济增长前景和货币政策，欧洲股市小幅上涨至 8 月历史高点。德国商业银行收复早盘跌幅，因收购可能性增加。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-23/european-stocks-muted-as-commerzbank-drops-on-deal-uncertainty</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 23 Sep 2024 07:15:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国股市守住涨势，收益率在 PMI 数据公布后攀升：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-22/asian-stocks-poised-to-fall-as-china-woes-worsen-markets-wrap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[数据显示美国商业活动增长放缓，美国股市继续上涨。在美联储上周降息半个百分点后，交易员们正在寻找进一步放松政策空间的新迹象。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-22/asian-stocks-poised-to-fall-as-china-woes-worsen-markets-wrap</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 22 Sep 2024 22:41:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
